Display Variable Details

Source: R/see.R
see.Rd

This function displays the following details of variable:

  • attributes (i.e. useful to inspect labels)

  • class, typeof, mode, storage.mode

  • table (frequency and percentage of values)

  • summary statistics

See is an S3 generic and currently works with objects of class 'character', 'factor', 'numeric', 'data.frame' and 'labelled'.

see(x)

codebook(x)

Arguments

x

The object to be displayed in the console.

Examples

see(mtcars$mpg)
